captions.text:
Everybody plays, two begin:
Luque and Andy...

What's the deal:
It's a game made of questions.
They can talk only through questions.

When someone slips, he's replaced,
and the questions go on.

The audience must give me a place.
You guys from my right.

Can't you see we are
together in this ship?
Do you know the pilot of that ship?
Is this what I'm talking now?
Could you take me to your leader?
You will take me to your planet?
Do you know what race am I?
Didn't you watch "Land of the Lost?"
Is it that show that only 30-year-olds know?
Are you ready for Britney Spears?
Guys, I just remembered, in that show...
She came in a flying saucer, man!
She's a pain in the ass even on other planets!
